    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>You cannot initialize an array like that. In addition to what others have suggested, you can do :</p>\n\n<pre><code>data[0] = 10;\ndata[1] = 20;\n...\ndata[9] = 91;\n</code></pre>\n"
